# Spec-first workflow (mandatory order)

1) Update @docs/spec.md
2) Update @docs/security.md if auth/authorization changes
3) Update @schemas/ if boundary data changed
4) Update @api/openapi.yaml if API contract changed (if present)
5) Write/Update tests
6) Implement code
7) Run validations until all green
